{"tid":1307510,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[忠言逆耳] 連儂牆搞埋呢個星期日唔好再搞","createTime":"2019-07-11T15:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:49:37.000Z","uid":41458,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9804d462e0cf75b2744e9daa7faea5bdf593f99c","tid":1307510,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連儂牆 與 佔路 性質基本上一樣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>好處</strong><br />\n- 可表達民意<br />\n- 有互相鼓舞作用<br />\n- 製造社區話題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>壞處</strong><br />\n- <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有對付佔路既方法都可以用於連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n- 易受襲, 打鳩你, 你報警又冇用, 轉個頭放人<br />\n- 長守難, 人少亦守唔住<br />\n- 耗資源<br />\n- 破壞易, 一人已可極速大量破壞幾日積落嚟既心血<br />\n<br />\n<strong>建議</strong><br />\n- <strong>IT人士建立網上連儂牆</strong><br />\n- 有需要時再PRINT出嚟好過<br />\n- 遊行時, 大家可以自己PRINT完帶出嚟"},{"pid":"1a1390ff6ecb4283eebc3c37c9525f39b7aca8f8","tid":1307510,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c517f64976c086ff6ef31ab1275ebb301d296","tid":1307510,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n乜撚都支持"},{"pid":"74d0f371b2e1f8c12f0aaa677b370fa8f4a2ae58","tid":1307510,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51b2908428a09fee2817648204c8cb8d8d54bb1","tid":1307510,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b089f4222f66c2b7a4f545a8ee042d217b6a2e4","tid":1307510,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.g